Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Day four of the Reapers' Game, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Will anything change if we survive this game? {Pronoun changed from I to we}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea if anything will change,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibuya's so diverse. You see all walks of life here. {Timing is WAY off for this sub}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's wrapped up in themselves, making a racket. {Everyone's always making a ruckus whenever they please}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! This is where you guys were hangin', huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls over by Ten-Four are gone today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat! Rhyme!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere else is blocked, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways whatcha guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you two are homies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We were people-watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That scanning shit freaks me out, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, there's so many people out there,  all thinking different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone's values are colliding at crazy speeds. {It's like a battleground where people's values clash with each other at a crazy rate}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know? Even though Shibuya's this crowded,  nobody notices us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel kinda lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to worry about others noticing me. {This + next line is said in passive form, which implies that he doesn't want people to notice him or talk to him, it's verbose but I added something that I thought would convey that. Without it, I think you can interpret these lines differently in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or about people trying to talk to me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with not having to talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you jus' said some real depressin' shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nothing good will come out of talking to strangers. {Alternatively; Yeah. There's no point in talking to strangers.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell what someone's thinking just by scanning them. It's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something... lonely about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that you should understand others by listening to what they have to say, though. {I actually think she's taking a jab at Neku here, so the "you" pronoun is important here since it can be interpreted as both general & direct advice}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stuffed animal's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Mr. Mew?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mew?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I made him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna touch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm! He's so soft and fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Shiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this outfit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a fashion designer. {Liberal, but works better with the next line}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous. I don't really know what it's like to have a dream. {The "I'm jealous" bit is implied in JP since she trails her sentence off but I made it explicit in the TL}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You "don't know"? Doesn't that just mean that you don't have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Phones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your temper, Beat! {This is actually a very good TL, don't touch this one}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Rhyme. You'll find a dream somewhere along the way if you just keep movin' forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it don't matter if you ain't got one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the best skateboarder in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll find a dream of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that pendant really rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I lined up for it with friends, but I couldn't get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a birthday present from my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You've got a great brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's super nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there's an event at Ten-Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's got everybody so worked up all of a sudden? {Alternatively: Hey, what's all the commotion about?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading toward Ten-Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no mission yet, so... Wanna check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ain't a mission, I ain't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait up, Beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Neku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's with this crowd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is normal for Ten-Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! They've got new outfits in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! These are totally cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eri, what do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to come here a lot with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Eiji Oji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really taken off recently thanks to his don't-give-a-damn attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All he did was drink water, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, "The Prince sells."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything Eiji Oji compliments sells out in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He even pushed that pendant Rhyme had on his blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you said you waited in line for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm a bit of a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to fashion, his comments are spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, you said that you made your own clothes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that they were store-bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I only did the sewing. The designs are Eri's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make clothes for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want lots of people to wear our clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want them to make people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mind if I take another look at that shop we passed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it. {Does anyone actually reply to this question with "No?" - is it just me that's the weird one?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're trying so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that if you survive these seven days,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your dream will come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Free Spain Hill from the Noise"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep coming! {Alternatively, "There's no end to 'em!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone is attracting the Noise here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku! Those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! You're totally mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I lie to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,—I'm telling you, I'm not mad! —So many Noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you let things get{\i1} that {\i0}bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like those two are the cause this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many we erase, more Noise keeps appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku, can you take out the Noise around them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they fighting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Mina was meeting with Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good. I'm pretty sure Ai's got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to surprise her might've backfired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to use Imprinting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:09:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It means using your Player pin to speak directly to people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, talk to each other and work this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about how you and Makoto have been meeting up in private!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught on? That figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you act so calm when—?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What're these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You two wanted go, right? To 777's concert. {Mistranslated in original TL}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always wanted to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Makoto and I were thinking up a surprise for your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I didn't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy getting tickets, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku! The Noise has stopped appearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those're the only ones left! {Alternatively; "Just have to clean these ones up, now"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,—Let me treat you to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,—And it looks like those two managed to make up. —Let me treat you to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,—And it looks like those two managed to make up. —For real? I want a parfait, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,—Friends help each other when they're sad or in trouble, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,—Eri, what're you doing later? —Friends can help each other when they're sad or in trouble, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's go that way, Neku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,—You haven't mentioned that girl lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,—Nothing. Just hurry. —You haven't mentioned that girl lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Shiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... kind of complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If something's on your mind, I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's because... in here... {Here refers to the UG}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Day five already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be much help today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? What's wrong—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dominate the Scramble Crossing view at 3:00."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dominate the view"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, that's just not enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Makoto. I know you'll make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're playing the ad here at 3:00 p.m. It's set in stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Set things up so everyone's eyes are locked on it for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But if we just play the video, everyone will walk right by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could that be today's mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that girl we passed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Eri. The one I told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute, and smart, and everyone likes her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I... wished I could be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wanted to cheer people up with the clothes you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're fine just the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clear this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But how exactly are we gonna clear this mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We use Eiji Oji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will listen if it comes from his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This water's totes delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince knows his stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,—That's that water from yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,—It's just water, right? —That's that water from yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,—I only got it because you waited in line for me, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,—Yup. We might learn something about Oji if we scan them. —I only got it because you waited in line for me, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,—Yup. We might learn something about Oji if we scan them. —I'm like, super happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Oji's holding an event at AMX later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving out all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher ups are pressuring me to spread 'em around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...these things look like red skulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's there another wall here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Center St." Why's there another wall here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already short on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we have to do to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no Noise around, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The requirements have been met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wall clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Take care of that pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to "take care of that pin," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There was light coming out of my pocket just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What pins do I have that you don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably that pin you got from that Reaper in the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, 777 is a Reaper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that means some Reapers are good guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why've you got two Player pins, Neku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Player Pins are supposed to be one per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know? I don't even know why I'm playing this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Having two might come in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if you put the spare pin in your chest pocket , it might stop a bullet, or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neku, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lost in thought, drinking this delicious water,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,when it hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Skull pins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if you all put these on, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it'd be the birth of a new trend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,—Come on, everybody! Let's start a trend together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,—Okay. —Come on, everybody! Let's start a trend together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use Imprinting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the giant screen on Q Front  at 3 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you all to put on the Red Skull pins,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go watch the giant screen at Q Front at 3 p.m.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be our little date. {Yakusoku literally means "promise" but it has a connotation of meeting up with someone at a given place or time, and the reason why all the girls scream here is because it has this connotation of a date}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch the giant screen at Scramble Crossing  at 3 p.m. today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd's started to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,—Hi there. —Those girls are... {Makoto says "Why are you—here)? but it's like the third subtitle here so you're gonna have to deal with it somehow}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. She found out about the surprise, and... {Removed the italics because that sounds mega condescending}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Two birds with one stone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 3 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no one warned me about that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't enough to clear the mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for. {Alternatively; We're going to get erased.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we cleared the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So... we're safe for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was different from the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of other Players got erased too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One wrong move, and we'd have joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saving my neck all day, Neku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're doing more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved that part-timer from back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and stopped those schoolgirls fighting yesterday—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we've made it here because you didn't abandon anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...you didn't give up on me, even after what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people have been saved 'cause of something that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Neku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In such a short time, you've changed quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...never want to screw up like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be fine, Neku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem down today, Eri. You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I know we're here to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do have something on your mind. Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,—I'm thinking of giving up designing completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,—Hey! —I'm thinking of giving up designing completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,—I'm thinking of giving up designing completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! You're so good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know, just scan her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could ever do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,—I loved the outfit you showed me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,—I'd feel like I'd be intruding on my friend's thoughts. —I loved the outfit you showed me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,—I'd feel like I'd be intruding on my friend's thoughts. —I want to see more of your designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,—It's not like she'll know. —I want to see more of your designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,—Thanks. —You're overcomplicating things. {He says "It's simple, isn't it?" with the implied meaning that I left in the TL}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought of finding out what Eri really thought of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say your dream was to be a fashion designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it without Shiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiki's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She turns the smallest ideas into complete items.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's skilled, considerate, and a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she had more talent than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't find the right way to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Shiki was worrying that she wasn't good at designing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"You don't have to be a designer", was what I wanted to tell her. {Alternatively, "You should do what you do best", was what I wanted to say.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But what came out was: "You're not meant to be a designer."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're a great seamstress, anyways."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologise right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to say sorry first thing the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can never see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The clothes I design only become real when Shiki makes them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't do it without Shiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... how she thought of me? {Not phrased like a question in JP but rhetorical because she's talking to herself out of disbelief}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to make lots of people happy with the clothes we made together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now... it still {\i1}is{\i0} our dream. {Present tense italicised to emphasise that the dream is not dead}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku, I'm sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come back to life and make clothes with Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? "Come back to life"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Reapers' Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My entry fee was my appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really look like I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how Eri looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reapers' Game is about testing Players to see who deserves a second chance at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Erased."
